{"level":"info","message":"{\n  \"table\": \"FAQs Improvement With AI\",\n  \"sample\": [\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"Is this tour safe, and what about emergencies?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"Yes, the tour operates with comfortable, air-conditioned vehicles and experienced drivers. For emergencies, your guide will assist you, and we recommend having travel insurance for peace of mind.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"What languages are available for this tour?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"Language availability is confirmed at booking.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"What are the main stops on this tour, and which museum do we visit?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"This tour takes you to Old Cairo’s Coptic landmarks like the Hanging Church, Saladin’s Citadel, and the Khan El-Khalili Bazaar. The museum included is the National Museum of Egyptian Civilization (NMEC), where you’ll see over 50,000 artifacts spanning 5,000 years of Egyptian history.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}","timestamp":"2026-05-02T11:46:50.834Z"}
{"level":"info","message":"Airtable smoke: TripFAQs -> sample_count=2","timestamp":"2026-05-02T11:46:51.494Z"}
{"level":"info","message":"{\n  \"table\": \"TripFAQs\",\n  \"sample\": [\n    {\n      \"Question\": \"What should I bring?\",\n      \"Answer\": \"Passport or ID card Sunglasses Camera Cash\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"Question\": \"What should I know before I go?\",\n      \"Answer\": \"This tour is available for customers staying in hotels in Cairo and Giza. Pickup time depends on your hotel location—please confirm the exact time one day before the trip. For inquiries, call or WhatsApp us. A pickup delay of up to 10 minutes may occur. The supplier will send your pickup time via email the day before the tour. Please provide full names of travelers and the room number via email.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}","timestamp":"2026-05-02T11:46:51.495Z"}
