{"level":"info","message":"{\n  \"table\": \"FAQs Improvement With AI\",\n  \"sample\": [\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"Are there optional extras or add-ons available?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"Yes, you can add an expert Egyptologist guide, and cultural Egyptian scarves during booking. These are optional and come at an extra charge, so you only pay for what you choose.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"What should I bring on this tour?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"Bring comfortable walking shoes, a hat, sunscreen, and your camera for photos.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"How much cash do I need for this tour?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"Bring some cash for tips, personal purchases, and any optional extras.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}","timestamp":"2026-05-02T13:29:04.503Z"}
