{"level":"info","message":"{\n  \"table\": \"FAQs Improvement With AI\",\n  \"sample\": [\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"What is the cancellation policy?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"You'll receive a full refund if you cancel at least 24 hours before the scheduled trip. Use the booking details provided after confirmation to cancel or reschedule.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"What kind of food is served for lunch?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"Lunch is an authentic Egyptian meal at a local restaurant. If you have dietary restrictions (e.g., vegetarian, gluten-free), you can request modifications when booking.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"Where and when is the hotel pickup?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"We provide convenient hotel pickup directly from your hotel lobby in the morning. Your guide will meet you there with comfortable air-conditioned transportation. You'll receive confirmation details after booking.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}","timestamp":"2026-05-03T22:57:11.611Z"}
