{"level":"info","message":"{\n  \"table\": \"FAQs Improvement With AI\",\n  \"sample\": [\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"What languages are available for the tour?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"Language availability is confirmed at booking.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"What optional extras can I add?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"You can add optional extras during booking. Options include an expert Egyptologist guide and cultural Egyptian scarves. These are available as add-ons at booking.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"How much walking is involved?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"The tour requires a moderate amount of walking across the museum, Citadel grounds, and Old Cairo streets. No special fitness level is needed, but comfortable shoes are essential. Vehicle transfers between major stops reduce fatigue.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}","timestamp":"2026-05-04T00:37:53.684Z"}
