{"level":"info","message":"{\n  \"table\": \"FAQs Improvement With AI\",\n  \"sample\": [\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"What is the cancellation policy?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"You'll receive a full refund if you cancel at least 24 hours before the scheduled trip. Use the booking details provided after confirmation to cancel or reschedule.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"Is this tour suitable for children and elderly travelers?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"Yes, the tour is generally suitable for all ages, but involves moderate walking. The vehicle is air-conditioned, and the pace is manageable. If you have specific mobility concerns, let us know at booking.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"What optional extras can I add?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"You can add optional extras during booking. Options include an expert Egyptologist guide and cultural Egyptian scarves. These are available as add-ons at booking.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}","timestamp":"2026-05-04T03:57:50.848Z"}
