{"level":"info","message":"{\n  \"table\": \"TripFAQs\",\n  \"sample\": [\n    {\n      \"Question\": \"What should I bring?\",\n      \"Answer\": \"Passport or ID card Sunglasses Camera Cash\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"Question\": \"What should I know before I go?\",\n      \"Answer\": \"This tour is available for customers staying in hotels in Cairo and Giza. Pickup time depends on your hotel location—please confirm the exact time one day before the trip. For inquiries, call or WhatsApp us. A pickup delay of up to 10 minutes may occur. The supplier will send your pickup time via email the day before the tour. Please provide full names of travelers and the room number via email.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}","timestamp":"2026-05-04T05:28:41.422Z"}
