{"level":"info","message":"{\n  \"table\": \"FAQs Improvement With AI\",\n  \"sample\": [\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"Which museum does this tour visit?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"This tour takes you to the National Museum of Egyptian Civilization (NMEC) in Fustat, not the Egyptian Museum in Tahrir or the Grand Egyptian Museum. At NMEC you'll see the Royal Mummies Hall and over 50,000 artifacts.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"How much walking is involved?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"The tour requires a moderate amount of walking across the museum, Citadel grounds, and Old Cairo streets. No special fitness level is needed, but comfortable shoes are essential. Vehicle transfers between major stops reduce fatigue.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"Where and when is the hotel pickup?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"We provide convenient hotel pickup directly from your hotel lobby in the morning. Your guide will meet you there with comfortable air-conditioned transportation. You'll receive confirmation details after booking.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}","timestamp":"2026-05-04T15:45:39.687Z"}
{"level":"info","message":"Airtable smoke: TripFAQs -> sample_count=2","timestamp":"2026-05-04T15:45:40.546Z"}
{"level":"info","message":"{\n  \"table\": \"TripFAQs\",\n  \"sample\": [\n    {\n      \"Question\": \"What should I bring?\",\n      \"Answer\": \"Passport or ID card Sunglasses Camera Cash\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"Question\": \"What should I know before I go?\",\n      \"Answer\": \"This tour is available for customers staying in hotels in Cairo and Giza. Pickup time depends on your hotel location—please confirm the exact time one day before the trip. For inquiries, call or WhatsApp us. A pickup delay of up to 10 minutes may occur. The supplier will send your pickup time via email the day before the tour. Please provide full names of travelers and the room number via email.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}","timestamp":"2026-05-04T15:45:40.548Z"}
