{"level":"info","message":"{\n  \"table\": \"FAQs Improvement With AI\",\n  \"sample\": [\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"How do I book the Luxor tour from Marsa Alam to the Valley of the Kings and Karnak Temples?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"You can book this guided experience directly through our website for instant confirmation. We recommend securing your spot in advance, especially during peak travel seasons, as our professional Egyptologist-led tours are popular. Once booked, you'll receive all the details you need for your day trip from Marsa Alam.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"Is lunch included and can you accommodate dietary restrictions?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"Yes, a delicious traditional Egyptian lunch at a local restaurant in Luxor is included, allowing you to savor authentic flavors. If you have specific dietary restrictions (vegetarian, gluten-free, etc.), please inform us at the time of booking so we can notify the restaurant. Soft drinks and bottled water are also provided during your transfers.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"AI_Question\": \"What happens if I need to cancel my booking?\",\n      \"AI_Answer\": \"If you need to cancel your booking, don’t worry—you can cancel at any time. You’ll receive a full refund if you cancel at least 24 hours before the scheduled trip. Please contact our customer service team and we’ll be happy to help you cancel or reschedule.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}","timestamp":"2026-05-05T12:57:05.708Z"}
