{"level":"info","message":"{\n  \"table\": \"TripFAQs\",\n  \"sample\": [\n    {\n      \"Question\": \"What should I know before I go?\",\n      \"Answer\": \"ickup locations: Available from hotels in Marsa Alam and El Quseir. Packed breakfast: Request a packed breakfast from your hotel reception one day before the trip. Traveler information: After booking, please provide all travelers' names, passport numbers, and your preferred hotel pickup time to the local partner.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"Question\": \"What should I bring?\",\n      \"Answer\": \"Passport or ID card Comfortable shoes Sunglasses\"\n    }\n  ]\n}","timestamp":"2026-05-05T15:41:35.292Z"}
