{"level":"info","message":"[\n  {\n    \"step_title\": \"Morning (30 minutes) – Hotel Pickup & Transfer to NMEC\",\n    \"step_description\": \"Your guide picks you up from your Cairo or Giza hotel in an air-conditioned vehicle and briefs you on the day ahead. This stress-free start ensures you arrive ready to explore. (Approx. 30 minutes)\",\n    \"step_label\": \"Morning\",\n    \"duration_value\": 30,\n    \"duration_unit\": \"minutes\",\n    \"meals_included\": \"None\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"step_title\": \"Morning (2 hours) – National Museum of Egyptian Civilization\",\n    \"step_description\": \"Explore NMEC's 50,000 artifacts, including the Royal Mummies Hall, where you'll see the preserved faces of pharaohs. This immersive journey through Egypt's past is a highlight of any Cairo sightseeing adventure. (Approx. 2 hours)\",\n    \"step_label\": \"Morning\",\n    \"duration_value\": 2,\n    \"duration_unit\": \"hours\",\n    \"meals_included\": \"None\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"step_title\": \"Late Morning (30 minutes) – Transfer to Saladin's Citadel\",\n    \"step_description\": \"Drive through Cairo's vibrant streets as your guide shares stories of the city's evolution from ancient times to the medieval era. The short ride builds anticipation for the panoramic views ahead. (Approx. 30 minutes)\",\n    \"step_label\": \"Late Morning\",\n    \"duration_value\": 30,\n    \"duration_unit\": \"minutes\",\n    \"meals_included\": \"None\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"step_title\": \"Late Morning (1 hour) – Saladin's Citadel & City Views\",\n    \"step_description\": \"Explore the 850-year-old fortress that once protected Cairo from crusaders, then soak in 360-degree views with the Pyramids on the horizon. This stop offers a perfect blend of history and photography opportunities. (Approx. 1 hours)\",\n    \"step_label\": \"Late Morning\",\n    \"duration_value\": 1,\n    \"duration_unit\": \"hours\",\n    \"meals_included\": \"None\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"step_title\": \"Lunch (1 hour) – Traditional Egyptian Meal\",\n    \"step_description\": \"Savor a delicious traditional Egyptian lunch at a local restaurant, featuring dishes like koshari, grilled meats, and fresh salads. This midday break recharges you for the afternoon's discoveries. (Approx. 1 hours)\",\n    \"step_label\": \"Lunch\",\n    \"duration_value\": 1,\n    \"duration_unit\": \"hours\",\n    \"meals_included\": \"Lunch\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"step_title\": \"Afternoon (30 minutes) – Transfer to Old Cairo\",\n    \"step_description\": \"Head south to the historic district of Old Cairo, where Coptic churches and Roman ruins line narrow lanes. Your guide points out landmarks along the way, weaving together stories of faith and resilience. (Approx. 30 minutes)\",\n    \"step_label\": \"Afternoon\",\n    \"duration_value\": 30,\n    \"duration_unit\": \"minutes\",\n    \"meals_included\": \"None\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"step_title\": \"Afternoon (1 hour) – Old Cairo & The Hanging Church\",\n    \"step_description\": \"Wander through ancient streets and visit the Hanging Church, one of the oldest Coptic Christian sites in Egypt, with its wooden roof suspended over a Roman fortress. This serene stop reveals a side of Cairo that many visitors miss. (Approx. 1 hours)\",\n    \"step_label\": \"Afternoon\",\n    \"duration_value\": 1,\n    \"duration_unit\": \"hours\",\n    \"meals_included\": \"None\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"step_title\": \"Late Afternoon (1 hour) – Khan El-Khalili Bazaar\",\n    \"step_description\": \"Lose yourself in the labyrinthine alleys of Cairo's most famous bazaar since the 14th century, browsing stalls of spices, lanterns, jewelry, and handcrafted souvenirs. This is the perfect place to haggle for unique treasures and soak in the lively atmosphere. (Approx. 1 hours)\",\n    \"step_label\": \"Late Afternoon\",\n    \"duration_value\": 1,\n    \"duration_unit\": \"hours\",\n    \"meals_included\": \"None\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"step_title\": \"Late Afternoon (30 minutes) – Return Transfer to Hotel\",\n    \"step_description\": \"Your tour concludes with a comfortable drop-off at your hotel, giving you time to relax and reflect on a day filled with ancient mummies, medieval fortresses, and bustling markets. You'll return with a deeper understanding of Cairo's layered history. (Approx. 30 minutes)\",\n    \"step_label\": \"Late Afternoon\",\n    \"duration_value\": 30,\n    \"duration_unit\": \"minutes\",\n    \"meals_included\": \"None\"\n  }\n]","timestamp":"2026-05-05T15:57:54.134Z"}
