{"level":"info","message":"[\n  {\n    \"question\": \"What is the cancellation policy?\",\n    \"answer\": \"You’ll receive a full refund if you cancel at least 24 hours before the scheduled trip. Use the booking details provided after confirmation to cancel or reschedule.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"question\": \"What should I bring on this Cairo day tour?\",\n    \"answer\": \"Bring comfortable walking shoes, a hat, sunscreen, and a camera for the Citadel views and museum exhibits. Carry some cash in Egyptian pounds for personal purchases at Khan El-Khalili bazaar, tips, or any optional extras included in your booking.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"question\": \"What languages are available for the guided tour?\",\n    \"answer\": \"Language availability is confirmed at booking. Please specify your preferred language when reserving.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"question\": \"Is this tour suitable for children or elderly travelers?\",\n    \"answer\": \"Yes, the tour is generally suitable for all ages, but it involves walking at the Citadel and through Old Cairo’s narrow streets. The NMEC is wheelchair-accessible, and the vehicle is air-conditioned. Let us know about any mobility needs at booking so we can assist.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"question\": \"What is included in the tour price?\",\n    \"answer\": \"Please refer to the 'What's Included' and 'What's included' sections on this page for a detailed list. Entrance-fee coverage and guiding depend on the option selected.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"question\": \"Which museum does this tour visit?\",\n    \"answer\": \"This tour takes you to the National Museum of Egyptian Civilization (NMEC) in Fustat, not the older Egyptian Museum in Tahrir or the Grand Egyptian Museum. At NMEC, you’ll see over 50,000 artifacts and the Royal Mummies Hall.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"question\": \"Where does the tour start and end?\",\n    \"answer\": \"The tour begins with a hotel pickup from your Cairo accommodation and ends with a drop-off at your hotel. The exact pickup time is confirmed after booking—just provide your hotel details when you reserve.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"question\": \"What food is included, and can dietary restrictions be accommodated?\",\n    \"answer\": \"Yes. Lunch is included as listed in What's Included.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"question\": \"What are the main stops on this tour?\",\n    \"answer\": \"Your Cairo day tour includes the National Museum of Egyptian Civilization (NMEC), Saladin’s Citadel with panoramic city views, Old Cairo’s Hanging Church, and Khan El-Khalili Bazaar. Lunch at a local restaurant is also part of the itinerary.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"question\": \"Can I customize the itinerary or skip a stop?\",\n    \"answer\": \"This is a fixed Cairo day tour designed to cover the highlights efficiently, but your guide can adjust the pace. If you need to skip a stop due to time or interest, just let your guide know.\"\n  }\n]","timestamp":"2026-05-05T15:57:58.595Z"}
